With this I could add a Service Impact Field, Product Management Impact, Technical Risk, Time to Implement, Manufacturing Impact, Safety Impact, etc.. and then in the Scoring Field (Field based on other values) I could calculate the score for each issue based on the individual scores multiplied by a scale factor for each type of issue. (Safey is X 10, Technical Risk is X 3 and Time to Implement is  X 1 etc...)  These scale factors should be integrated into the new calculation field.

